---
source: starstream-compiler/src/typecheck/tests.rs
description: "Source:\n\nfn test() {\n    let x: Result<i64, bool> = Result::Ok(42);\n}\n"
---
T-Fn: test => ()
  T-Let: {test: fn() -> () [test]} ⊢ let x: Result<i64, bool> = Result::Ok(42); ⇒ Result<i64, bool>
    T-Call: {test: fn() -> () [test]} ⊢ Result::Ok(42) ⇒ Result
      T-Var: {test: fn() -> () [test]} ⊢ Result::Ok ⇒ fn(t1) -> Result [0]
      T-Int: {test: fn() -> () [test]} ⊢ 42 ⇒ i64
      Unify-Var: i64 ~ t1 => {i64/t3}
    Unify-Enum: Result<i64, bool> ~ Result => {bool/t2, i64/t1}
      Unify-Var: bool ~ t2 => {bool/t2}
      Unify-Var: i64 ~ i64 => {i64/t1}
